## Teamcenter Media

### Base Media

Required location: `C:\tc_media_files\tc2412_wntx64\tc2412_wntx64`

Key contents to verify after extracting:

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `tem.bat` | TEM launcher |
| `install\` | TEM install logic and help |
| `tc\` | Teamcenter binaries |
| `Web_tier\` | IIS web tier deployment |
| `portal\` | Rich client portal |
| `bmide\` | BMIDE |

### Patch Media

Required location: `C:\tc_media_files\Tc2412.0008_wntx64\wntx64`

The patch is registered in `C:\TC2412\install\configuration.xml` as:

- Parent version: `2412`
- Patch version: `2412.8`

### TEM Solution Entry Points

The base media exposes these solution files under `install\solution_*.xml`:

| File | Use |
|------|-----|
| `solution_corpserv.xml` | **Corporate server — use this for the primary install** |
| `solution_awserver.xml` | Active Workspace server-side |
| `solution_awclient.xml` | Active Workspace client-side |
| `solution_bmide.xml` | BMIDE install path |
| `solution_richclient4t.xml` | 4-tier rich client |
| `solution_multisite.xml` | Multisite deployment |

For this host pattern, always start with `solution_corpserv.xml`.
